# Entity Patterns

## Base Entity
All entities inherit from `BaseEntity<TKey>`:
```csharp
public class ShortenLink : BaseEntity<long>
{
    public string SourceLink { get; set; }
    public string ShortenPath { get; set; }
}
```

## Factory Methods
Entities should have static factory methods for creation:
```csharp
public static ShortenLink Create(string sourceLink, string shortenPath)
    => new ShortenLink
    {
        CreatedAt = DateTime.UtcNow,
        CreatedBy = "System",
        ShortenPath = shortenPath,
        SourceLink = sourceLink,
    };
```

## Interfaces
Entities implement standard interfaces:
- `IEntityId<TKey>` → Provides `Id` property
- `IAuditableEntity` → Provides `CreatedAt`, `CreatedBy`
